<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>手机充值</title>
	<meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-siteapp" /><!-- 百度禁止转码 -->
	<meta name="keywords" content="这里写关键字">
	<meta name="description" content="这里写页面描述">
	<meta name ="viewport" content ="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, user-scalable=no"> 
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no" /> <!-- 禁止自动识别为电话号码和邮件 -->
	<script src="../../public/js/jquery.js"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../public/css/base.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-inverse">
	<section class="container bg-f">
		<section class="form-group">
			<label class="form-label" for="payPw1">手机号码</label>
			<div class="form-control-box" wx-role="empty-input">
				<input class="form-control" id="phone1" type="text" maxlength="11" placeholder="请输入手机号码">
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="form-group">
			<label class="form-label" for="payPw2">确认号码</label>
			<div class="form-control-box" wx-role="empty-input">
				<input class="form-control" id="phone2" type="text" maxlength="11" placeholder="请再次输入手机号码">
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="form-group">
			<label class="form-label" for="payPwAgain">面值</label>
			<div class="form-control-box">
				<input class="form-control" id="payPwAgain" type="text" placeholder="请输入50的倍数，上限为500">
				<span class="money">元</span>
			</div>
		</section>
	</section>
	<section class="container">
		<p class="light lh20 mt6">需收取3%的服务费</p>
		<button class="btn btn-primary mt25" id="sure">确定</button>
		<p class="mt16 dark">温馨提示</p>
		<p class="light lh20">月初月末为充值高峰，话费到账可能会延迟或失败，建议错时充值。如若充值失败将退回积分，敬请谅解，感谢支持！</p>
	</section>
	<a href="javascript:;" class="tabulation">
		<img src="img/detail.png" class="mt6" width="20" height="24">
	</a>
	<section class="prepaid border-t flexbox hide">
		<div class="flex-1">
			<button class="btn btn-default btn-xs">充值记录</button>
		</div>
	</section>
</body>
<script src="../../public/js/base.js"></script>
<script src="../../public/js/gat.AlertMessage.js"></script>
<script>
    window.onload= function(){

        $('#phone1').blur(function(){
            var str = $(this).val();
            var re = /^1\d{10}$/;
            if (!re.test(str)){
	            message.showNotify({
		            'content':'无效的手机号！',
		            'delay': '1000'
		        });
            }
        })

        $('#phone2').blur(function(){
            var str = $(this).val();
            if (str != $('#phone1').val()){
	            message.showNotify({
		            'content':'两次输入不一致！',
		            'delay': '1000'
		        });
            }
        })

        $('#payPwAgain').blur(function(){
        	if ($(this).val() > 500) {
	            message.showNotify({
		            'content':'充值上限为500元！',
		            'delay': '1000'
		        });
        	}
        })
    }
</script>
</html>
